              <h4>Chi Tiết Cố Định Đầu Trục Tiện CNC</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/vi/products/precision-machined-parts/milled-front-inner-fixing-plate-paper-roll-guide-rail" class="related-slide-card" data-key="milled-front-inner-fixing-plate-paper-roll-guide-rail">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/milled-front-inner-fixing-plate-paper-roll-guide-rail.jpg" alt="Tấm Cố Định Trong Phía Trước Phay Ray Dẫn Cuộn Giấy" loading="lazy" />
              <h4>Tấm Cố Định Trong Phía Trước Phay Ray Dẫn Cuộn Giấy</h4>
            </a>
            <a href="/vi/products/precision-machined-parts/precision-bearing-bracket-cnc-milled" class="related-slide-card" data-key="precision-bearing-bracket-cnc-milled">
              <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/precision-bearing-bracket-cnc-milled.jpg" alt="Giá Đỡ Ổ Bi Chính Xác (Phay CNC)" loading="lazy" />
